# ABDS META - Development work on the specification itself
# This repository follows the two-repository pattern:
#   - Root level = STANDARD (what users download)
#   - .abds/ = META (how we develop the spec - dogfooding ABDS on ABDS)
# We keep our development process private to maintain clean distribution.
# Users get the spec, not our internal discussions.
.abds/

